<br>
Baldur's Gate II is based on AD&amp;D 2nd Edition while NWN is based on 3rd Edition rules.   That means the spells will be different and how they operate will vary as well.<br>
<br>
On top of all of that, not all the AD&amp;D 3rd Edition spells will be implemented in NWN.  Bioware has stated that some of those spells just don't translate well into a computer game environment.<br>
<br>
That beign said, if you do your homework on the 3rd Edition information, and then read the rules that will come with NWN, you should be well versed in all the spells of the game.<br>
<br>
--Robert<br>
